                <!-- 담보대출 -->
                <section class="basis-section last-section">
                    <div class="section-inner">

                        <div class="content-panel type_panel-loan">
                            <div class="panel-header">
<%--                                <p>Seoul Auction provides loans using art and antiques as collateral. We hope for your interest in the collectors.</p>--%>
                                <p>Seoul Auction offers loans to art owners that are based on artworks and/or antiques as collateral..</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="panel-body">
                                <!-- [0516]레이아웃변경 -->
                                <article class="loan-step-area">
                                    <div class="help-box">
                                        <i class="icon-inquiry"></i>
<%--                                    <span>If the subject of the e-mail contains the word collateral or loan, it becomes a spam e-mail and is difficult to check.</span>--%>
                                        <span>Emails on art financing sent to Seoul Auction should not include the word “collateral” or “loan” in the title, as this usually causes the email to be automatically classified as spam (and possibly never being read).</span>
                                    </div>

                                    <div class="loan-step loan-step-other">
                                        <div class="item-area">
                                            <div class="item-header">
                                                <div class="icon-box">
                                                    <i class="icon-loan_recvemail"></i>
                                                </div>
                                                <div class="title ft_b">
                                                    <span>STEP 01</span>
<%--                                                    <b class="tt3">Send Email</b>--%>
                                                    <b class="tt3">Application via email</b>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                            <div class="item-body tb1">
<%--                                                <p>Send images and artwork information by email</p>--%>
                                                <p>Photo and information on the artwork is sent by email to Seoul Auction.</p>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="item-area">
                                            <div class="item-header">
                                                <div class="icon-box">
                                                    <i class="icon-loan_recvemail"></i>
                                                </div>
                                                <div class="title ft_b">
                                                    <span>STEP 02</span>
<%--                                                    <b class="tt3">Specialist’s Reply</b>--%>
                                                    <b class="tt3">Sending of reply on loan viability</b>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                            <div class="item-body tb1">
<%--                                                <p>The specialist in charge appraises the artwork and replies with the availability of lending.</p>--%>
                                                <p>After an assessment of whether a collateral loan can be provided for the artwork, an email is sent by the employee in charge.</p>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="item-area">
                                            <div class="item-header">
                                                <div class="icon-box">
                                                    <i class="icon-loan_glass"></i>
                                                </div>
                                                <div class="title ft_b">
                                                    <span>STEP 03</span>
<%--                                                    <b class="tt3">Artwork Valuation</b>--%>
                                                    <b class="tt3">Valuation of artwork</b>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                            <div class="item-body">
<%--                                                <p>Receive the original artwork and appraises the authenticity and price.</p>--%>
                                                <p>After the artwork (physical version) is received, an assessment of its authenticity and price is conducted.</p>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="item-area">
                                            <div class="item-header">
                                                <div class="icon-box">
                                                    <i class="icon-loan_phone"></i>
                                                </div>
                                                <div class="title ft_b">
                                                    <span>STEP 04</span>
<%--                                                    <b class="tt3">Notify Confirmation</b>--%>
                                                    <b class="tt3">Sending of reply on whether loan will be provided</b>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                            <div class="item-body">
<%--                                                <p>Confirm the availability of collateral loans.</p>--%>
                                                <p>An email is sent on whether the sender has been approved for the desired loan.</p>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="item-area">
                                            <div class="item-header">
                                                <div class="icon-box">
                                                    <i class="icon-document"></i>
                                                </div>
                                                <div class="title ft_b">
                                                    <span>STEP 05</span>
<%--                                                    <b class="tt3">Visit and Submit</b>--%>
                                                    <b class="tt3">In-person submission of documents</b>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                            <div class="item-body">
<%--                                                <p>Fill out the paperwork and visit Seoul Auction to submit the form.</p>--%>
                                                <p>An in-person visit is made to a Seoul Auction location to submit the required documents (based on customer type: individual or corporate).</p>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="item-area">
                                            <div class="item-header">
                                                <div class="icon-box">
                                                    <i class="icon-loan_money"></i>
                                                </div>
                                                <div class="title ft_b">
                                                    <span>STEP 06</span>
<%--                                                    <b class="tt3">Guide for Deposit</b>--%>
                                                    <b class="tt3">Sending of funds (with guidelines/explanatory letter)</b>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                            <div class="item-body">
<%--                                                <p>After deliberation of the paperwork, the loan is paid within a week.</p>--%>
                                                <p>After the document screening is completed, the funds are wired within one week (accompanied by explanatory letter/list of guidelines regarding loan).</p>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </article>
