                                <article class="loan-document-area">
                                    <div class="loan-document">
                                        <div class="item-area item-area-seq-1">
                                            <div class="item-header">
<%--                                                <div class="tt3">Preparation of documents for personal customer</div>--%>
                                                <div class="tt3">Required documents: individual customer</div>
                                            </div>
                                            <div class="item-body">
                                                <ul class="dot tb1">
<%--                                                    <li>Personal legal seal (stamp)</li>--%>
<%--                                                    <li>Certification of personal legal (within to 3 months)</li>--%>
<%--                                                    <li>Photocopy of identification </li>--%>
<%--                                                    <li>Photocopy of money passbook</li>--%>
<%--                                                    <li>Certification of amount of income (National Tax Service)</li>--%>
<%--                                                    <li>Certification of full payment (National Tax Service)</li>--%>
<%--                                                    <li>Certification of council taxes (district office)</li>--%>
                                                    <li>Personal seal</li>
                                                    <li>1 copy of personal seal validity certificate (issued within past three months)</li>
                                                    <li>1 copy of legal ID</li>
                                                    <li>1 copy of bankbook</li>
                                                    <li>1 Certificate of Earned Income (National Tax Service)</li>
                                                    <li>1 Payment Verification form (National Tax Service)</li>
                                                    <li>1 Proof of Local Tax Payment (Community Service Center)</li>
                                                </ul>
                                                <div class="refer tb2">
<%--                                                    <p>Any default of national taxes is unavailable to apply.</p>--%>
<%--                                                    <p> Disapproval loan if at least one document is not exist.</p>--%>
                                                    <p>If you have overdue taxes, your application will not be accepted.</p>
                                                    <p>Your loan will not be authorized unless all of the above documents have been presented. Please make sure to submit all required documents.</p>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="item-area only-pc">
                                            <div class="item-header">
<%--                                                <div class="tt3">Type of collateral</div>--%>
                                                <div class="tt3">Types of collateral accepted</div>
                                            </div>
                                            <div class="item-body">
<%--                                                <p class="tb1">artwork available for auction</p>--%>
<%--                                                <p class="tb2">(Example) Modern and contemporary Art, antiques (Except for Chinese ceramics)</p>--%>
                                                <p class="tb1">Artworks that can be sold through an auction</p>
                                                <p class="tb2">E.g. works of modern/contemporary art, works of ancient art (excluding Chinese ceramics)</p>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="loan-document">
                                        <div class="item-area">
                                            <div class="item-header">
<%--                                                <div class="tt3">Preparation of documents for business corporation</div>--%>
                                                <div class="tt3">Required documents: corporate customer</div>
                                            </div>
                                            <div class="item-body">
                                                <ul class="dot tb1">
<%--                                                    <li>Certified photocopy of registration/license</li>--%>
<%--                                                    <li>Certification of corporate of legal seal (within to 3 months)</li>--%>
<%--                                                    <li>Corporate of legal seal</li>--%>
<%--                                                    <li>Certified copy of corporate of the register (within 3 months)</li>--%>
<%--                                                    <li>Certified copy of personal of the register (within 3 months)</li>--%>
<%--                                                    <li>Photocopy of identification (president CEO)</li>--%>
<%--                                                    <li>Photocopy of conference of directors</li>--%>
<%--                                                    <li>Photocopy of money passbook</li>--%>
<%--                                                    <li>A statement of audit (past year)</li>--%>
<%--                                                    <li>Imposing tax of assessments of statement (past year)</li>--%>
<%--                                                    <li>Certification of detailed imposing tax and payment of tax</li>--%>
                                                    <li>Copy of business license</li>
                                                    <li>1 copy of corporate seal validity certificate (issued within past three months)</li>
                                                    <li>Corporate seal, CEO’s seal, and certified copy of corporate register (issued within past three months)</li>
                                                    <li>Validity certificate for CEO’s seal (issued within past three months)</li>
                                                    <li>Copy of legal ID (of CEO or representative)</li>
                                                    <li>Copy of board of directors’ meeting minutes</li>
                                                    <li>Copy of bankbook</li>
                                                    <li>Previous year’s audit report</li>
                                                    <li>Previous year’s Certificate of VAT Tax Base</li>
                                                    <li>Tax Assessment Certificate and Certificate of Tax Payment</li>
                                                </ul>
                                                <div class="refer tb2">
<%--                                                    <p>If a person representing the president CEO : 1. Identification of your representative, 2. Legal seal of letter of attorney</p>--%>
<%--                                                    <p>Disapproval loan if at least one document is not exist. </p>--%>
                                                    <p>If your application is submitted by proxy, 1. the proxy’s ID and a 2. sealed power of attorney are also required.</p>
                                                    <p>Your loan will not be authorized unless all of the above documents have been presented. Please make sure to submit all required documents.</p>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </article>

